Root is a parent elements and Node is child elements of parent Node (The parent node is Root).

Node store information and other node connection the parent node.

Root: Root has no parent.(Root has main parent).

Parent Node: parent node is a Immediate Predecessor.(immediate predecessor means That is it's parent node)

Leaf Node: There has no child node.

Non Leaf Node: There are at last one node in this parent node.(Internal Node)

Path: Sequence of connection of edges.(edges = node)

Ancestor: Root node predecessor.   (Predecessor working up to down step.)

Decendent: Root node successor.  (Seccessor working down to up step.)

Sibligns: Children are form same parent node.